Class GenericElementNode<T>

java.lang.Object
solution.listadt.GenericElementNode<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
GenericListADTNode<T>
public class GenericElementNode<T> extends Object implements GenericListADTNode<T>
This is a non-empty node in a generic list. It contains the object data and the rest of the list
